# 🗺️ Kiosk Intelligence Platform

Live dashboard for monitoring kiosk performance across Canada.

🔗 **Live Demo:** https://logiclegion.github.io/kiosk-dashboard/

## Features
- 📊 Real-time risk scoring
- 💰 Daily revenue loss tracking ($286/day current)
- 🍁 Canada-only data filtering
- 📎 Export to Power BI / Tableau

## Built With
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Chart.js, Leaflet
- GitHub Pages
